Make sure there are no stray spaces in your 1.14.3 regex. Use the 
frontier report or other status info to make sure there are still URIs 
queued.

Also, I don't think the reluctant qualifier ('?') is adding anything 
here; you might as well use "^.*$" or even just ".*" if your aim is to 
list all.

- Gordon @ IA
